{"tid":180601,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得陌生人嘅安慰先係最好","createTime":"2017-03-31T04:36:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-31T15:25:40.000Z","uid":78777,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9830dc12f1327f52d48925b3326c724b8137d98","tid":180601,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:36:06.000Z","msg":"最近好唔開心，成日會去草地/海傍散下心，坐係草地望住人或者望下海咁<br />\n之後有一次有個陌生人過咗嚟問我做咩喊，我咩都無講，佢就坐係我隔離畀紙巾我，等到我好啲先至講句加油先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比起一啲唔理我死活嘅&quot;朋友&quot;我覺得陌生人嘅安慰更加安慰到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:巴"},{"pid":"83fa61a8bc466f3fa4f326071b54e47d64112805","tid":180601,"uid":23339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最近好唔開心，成日會去草地/海傍散下心，坐係草地望住人或者望下海咁<br />\n之後有一次有個陌生人過咗嚟問我做咩喊，我咩都無講，佢就坐係我隔離畀紙巾我，等到我好啲先至講句加油先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比起一啲唔理我死活嘅&quot;朋友&quot;我覺得陌生人嘅安慰更加安慰到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:巴</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔好咁讚我啦。<br />\n<br />\n其實果晚我都想喊，<br />\n但你霸住咗我個位，等極又唔肯走。<br />\n我又驚當面講出黎會尷尬，<br />\n所以最後你唔走我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做人積極啲，<br />\n唔好再諗埋啲負面野，<br />\n咁樣自己都會舒服啲。<br />\n<br />\n下次唔好再走黎霸住我個位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"7cb9e041fc3e97787c06665665838a66fbb1e7db","tid":180601,"uid":46894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:51:06.000Z","msg":"冇任何連帶關係嘅人係最好傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb9adfbe38883f4d642047c04e4383c91628d1ad","tid":180601,"uid":78777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:51:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最近好唔開心，成日會去草地/海傍散下心，坐係草地望住人或者望下海咁<br />\n之後有一次有個陌生人過咗嚟問我做咩喊，我咩都無講，佢就坐係我隔離畀紙巾我，等到我好啲先至講句加油先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比起一啲唔理我死活嘅&quot;朋友&quot;我覺得陌生人嘅安慰更加安慰到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申:巴</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唔好咁讚我啦。<br />\n<br />\n其實果晚我都想喊，<br />\n但你霸住咗我個位，等極又唔肯走。<br />\n我又驚當面講出黎會尷尬，<br />\n所以最後你唔走我走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做人積極啲，<br />\n唔好再諗埋啲負面野，<br />\n咁樣自己都會舒服啲。<br />\n<br />\n下次唔好再走黎霸住我個位<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油</blockquote><br />\n我晏晝去㗎wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d967b35bacdf69135edbd0c6bec0c1bb602c2fba","tid":180601,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T04:59:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇任何連帶關係嘅人係最好傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺"},{"pid":"e4a1ada90142468f401cf392526fd2ff66bc1c33","tid":180601,"uid":29645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T12:48:07.000Z","msg":"一望海就眼濕濕"},{"pid":"474618e04ddcac449d6cce23dd6d40cfc5055ff7","tid":180601,"uid":63132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T15:25:40.000Z","msg":"試過比陌生人安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣真係超唔開心,<br />\n其實都係想有個人聽下你講野姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}